metadata.description:
"Cobo 4th Anniversary NFT" is an exclusive limited edition of NFT, created in 1,000 copies to thank all the people who have been contributing to the crypto world.

Just as the gorgeous underwater world contains huge energy and infinite possibilities, the charm of the encrypted world has attracted countless creators to build a rich on chain ecology. For innovation and exploration, the builders are indomitable.

NFT owners are important contributors to the ecology of the crypto world. Each owner will get one copy of NFT work with a unique identity number, paying tribute to the builders of every tiny attempt and revolutionary innovation made for the crypto world.
